This paper deals with the problem of Unsupervised Domain Translation, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper proposes a new framework based on Optimal Transport (OT), which is a mathematical concept that is often used in computer vision and graphics (cs.GR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning techniques, which is a common theme in neural networks (cs.NE).
